"aspect_ratio": 0.56, "filesize_approx": 44941064, "http_headers": {"User-Agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/93.0.4556.0 Safari/537.36", "Accept": "text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8", "Accept-Language": "en-us,en;q=0.5", "Sec-Fetch-Mode": "navigate", "Referer": "https://www.instagram.com/"}, "video_ext": "mp4", "audio_ext": "none", "abr": 0, "vbr": 2371.044, "format": "dash-1650593925935428v - 1080x1920 (DASH video)"}], "title": "Video by youranxietyislying2yew", "description": "Can I talk to your inner child?", "duration": 151.633, "timestamp": 1773528000, "uploader_id": "48593623545", "uploader": "Ryan Primer", "channel": "youranxietyislying2yew", "like_count": 124371, "comment_count": 6463, "comments": [{"author": "acetheartcat", "author_id": "78831705287", "id": "18099246667803888", "text": "As a person with DID who immediately let their child trauma-holder front to hear this, thank you. They almost started sobbing but I think they really needed that.", "timestamp": 1775354948}, {"author": "trinkets_by_tink", "author_id": "184199507", "id": "17951599829966108", "text": "😭🥺🥺🥺❤️ you got me at 'hey kiddo'", "timestamp": 1775353268}, {"author": "egnssoirs", "author_id": "13125939265", "id": "17860881534622086", "text": "oh, i’m crying now", "timestamp": 1775351657}, {"author": "strawberriesandsunshinee", "author_id": "25550886", "id": "18080533169617731", "text": "“i’m outside, you hear the birds? we love it out here, it’s our favorite spot” hit me haaaaard while i’m sitting outside in my “safe place” now sobbing", "timestamp": 1775347399}, {"author": "itzunknown710ttv", "author_id": "40869758731", "id": "17911083636182958", "text": "", "timestamp": 1775347294}, {"author": "ciaraa193", "author_id": "18613591824", "id": "18100796290980368", "text": "The “hey kiddo” immediately got me, idky but I started crying", "timestamp": 1775346419}, {"author": "amxnv.mvridi", "author_id": "1388445145", "id": "17929697595251461", "text": "❤️‍🩹❤️‍🩹😭😭😭😭😭😢😢🥺🥹", "timestamp": 1775345478}, {"author": "blankawho", "author_id": "10413883300", "id": "17955974937092208", "text": "Man, that was so so beautiful, I couldn't stop the emotions. It is a great reminder that we can do things differently; thank you 💜✨", "timestamp": 1775343754}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/652387177_26245791691719020_6977981402082447792_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4LmRlZmF1bHRfY292ZXJfZnJhbWUuYzIifQ&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=108&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gF-xBIU1_M3AN9wfp1vzbM7HBdHsDeVtnoZIeRZjeYCHl8wcu4UdTXisbMuy6Bu5o4&_nc_ohc=WJyM8VC2VM8Q7kNvwEl3q8X&_nc_gid=dGx6R-RozwDSQKvJ4Tm7PQ&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af1tMmm45P5khsuJHi3IYLMq06BfTuxSEwJ7xAYSxwWW9A&oe=69D78BED&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 640, "height": 1136, "id": "0", "resolution": "640x1136"}, {"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/652387177_26245791691719020_6977981402082447792_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4LmRlZmF1bHRfY292ZXJfZnJhbWUuYzIifQ&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=108&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gF-xBIU1_M3AN9wfp1vzbM7HBdHsDeVtnoZIeRZjeYCHl8wcu4UdTXisbMuy6Bu5o4&_nc_ohc=WJyM8VC2VM8Q7kNvwEl3q8X&_nc_gid=dGx6R-RozwDSQKvJ4Tm7PQ&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af1tMmm45P5khsuJHi3IYLMq06BfTuxSEwJ7xAYSxwWW9A&oe=69D78BED&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 750, "height": 1331, "id": "1", "resolution": "750x1331"}, {"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/652387177_26245791691719020_6977981402082447792_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4LmRlZmF1bHRfY292ZXJfZnJhbWUuYzIifQ&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=108&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gF-xBIU1_M3AN9wfp1vzbM7HBdHsDeVtnoZIeRZjeYCHl8wcu4UdTXisbMuy6Bu5o4&_nc_ohc=WJyM8VC2VM8Q7kNvwEl3q8X&_nc_gid=dGx6